13.31	A_Course_In_Miracles	A Course in Miracles	A Course in Miracles is a self-study curriculum that aims to assist its readers in achieving spiritual transformation. The book describes a purely non-dualistic philosophy of forgiveness and includes what are meant to be practical lessons and applications for the practice of forgiveness in one's daily life. The introduction to the book contains the following summary, "Nothing real can be threatened. Nothing unreal exists. Herein lies the peace of God."	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ec/ACIM3COVER.jpg/110px-ACIM3COVER.jpg
